Title: Authorizes the town of Webster, county of Monroe to alienate certain lands used as parkland by the Candlewood Park District and to dedicate certain other lands as parkland
Summary: Authorizes the town of Webster, county of Monroe, to alienate certain lands used as parkland by the Candlewood Park District and to dedicate certain other lands as parkland for use by the Bear Creek park district.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to authorizing the town of Webster, county of Monroe, to alienate certain lands used as parkland by the Candlewood Park District and to dedicate certain other lands as parklands for use by the Bear Creek Park District
